```And `blueprint.css` adds:
```css
.sbs-lean-column {
  min-width: 0;
  overflow-wrap: break-word;
  word-wrap: break-word;
  overflow-x: auto;
  position: relative;
}

.sbs-lean-column pre.lean-code {
